@eric-wieser, I have updated the PR: I think that this addresses all the cases of `Co*variantClass X X ...`.

The cases where the two types `X` are different actually benefit from eta-reduction, so I left them untouched.

Also, there were a couple of instance of `(swap) HDiv` in `Order/Filter/Pointwise`.

